{"tid":2458110,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"其實真係冇必要借緬甸既抗爭黎到踩鳩香港人～","createTime":"2021-03-23T07:32:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T07:53:12.000Z","uid":219007,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"67cd6ec731cbd6e7bc735040f38c4acba462108b","tid":2458110,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T07:32:06.000Z","msg":"緬甸醞釀緊武裝革命，成唔成功未知，但係已經有人想借緬甸黎踩香港人，其實我想問：踩黎為乜呢？<br />\n<br />\n我先撇除你係有心刻意咁做，即係可能係五毛或者純粹放負。 就當你真心對香港人恨鐵不成鋼，但我想問吓，乜你今日先知香港係咁？ 要到目睹緬甸既勇敢先至明白整體香港人嘅懦弱？其實你會唔會遲咗啲？<br />\n<br />\n唔係話想批評香港人啲乜嘢，事關香港人做唔到佢哋呢一步係有原因。 係一個極度資本主義嘅社會下人人隨時萬幾兩萬蚊人工，周街都係大學畢業生，中產可以十幾萬蚊一個月，個個生活多姿多彩，物質豐富，種種嘅原因令抗爭有所代價，香港不嬲都係咁㗎啦，呢個係鐵一般嘅事實。如果一個緬甸人生活喺香港呢種環境我都相信都會變成咁。<br />\n<br />\n你仲要未計仲有移民呢條出路，走難仲可以揀頭等Tim，咁試問點解要仲要去衝？ 呢一樣係一個好現實同實際嘅問題，無論你點樣屌佢都唔會解決得到，所以亦都解釋到點解香港永遠都做唔到你哋心目中嗰種抗爭程度。 而你哋喺到恨鐵不成鋼，不斷借緬甸人抽香港人水其實反映出你哋只係條氣唔順，亦都因為太年輕而未明白香港係一個咩地方。 <br />\n<br />\n我覺得後生會再出嚟再打過，因為佢哋而家純粹唔忿氣。但係只限於一班更加後生嘅人會出嚟，而到是會出聲嘅大人係更加少，而整個客觀效果就係青少年死得更慘。呢個就係你哋嘅將來。<br />\n<br />\n接受唔到就對自己好啲離開，再喺度意氣用事恨鐵不成鋼都冇意思，呢個就係我對你哋細路嘅勸告。少年你真係太年輕了。"},{"pid":"96e56464d6eae78af055063cf9cf73d250ef2cf3","tid":2458110,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T07:35:17.000Z","msg":"連登大把踩港撚<br />\n剩係識得攞住個keyboard打柒人"},{"pid":"ef89f3d6dbd160d574cb925c09a38dded3808a69","tid":2458110,"uid":114193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T07:36:13.000Z","msg":"咪係，做港豬最好<br />\n支持連sir 表忠論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n手足唔能夠再情緒用事，大家只得 表忠 / 離開 兩條路你揀。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gLganT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gLganT</a><br />\n中大DQ學生會一事足以證明只能放棄香港，留底只能夠選擇表忠。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2423210\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2423210</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n等我copy連下sir 嘅大作你哋睇<br />\n震懾下你班連登黑暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老實問，香港人係咪已經開始習慣？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2443437\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2443437</a><br />\n「安心出行」根本就冇得避，留底既香港人只會能夠接受<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2401117\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2401117</a><br />\n依家講到明連選舉都唔俾你玩，請問啲留港抗爭撚點睇？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2417881\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2417881</a><br />\n［改變心態］香港變成點唔重要，最緊要自己活得開心就足夠！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2368342\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2368342</a>"},{"pid":"ff4333bf68e9af24d7d84469d57b87b3e86512f7","tid":2458110,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T07:39:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f7be895ad6eeaffe1e56d1aae23a7c083bce75","tid":2458110,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T07:43:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e4610b1b231793389e157b4c237363d279ed03","tid":2458110,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T07:48:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21255750fad12fbe93abbec12caea691955f6a6d","tid":2458110,"uid":114193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T07:49:35.000Z","msg":"另：連sir精選文集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聖誕節，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2329311/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2329311/page/1</a><br />\n肥佬黎俾人告國安法，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2323506/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2323506/page/1</a><br />\n中大畢業遊行，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2315353/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2315353/page/1</a><br />\n拜登贏咗，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2276817/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2276817/page/1</a><br />\n就黎國安法實行，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2184746/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2184746/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2073990/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2073990/page/1</a><br />\n612一周年，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2046361/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2046361/page/1</a><br />\n有武肺，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1850160/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1850160/page/1</a><br />\nPoly 打完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1768364/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1768364/page/1</a><br />\n要選區議會，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1681018/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1681018/page/1</a><br />\n機場壓力測試完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1548844/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1548844/page/1</a><br />\n8月大罷工完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1417635/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1417635/page/1</a><br />\n728元朗遊行完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1383029/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1383029/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"ee75fa8afcea79c2bdc95afa3a802fd2162363bc","tid":2458110,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T07:53:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}